Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.35,0:01:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护接受了上级贵族霞大路家的公主琉璃千代的保镖一职
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与企图篡夺霞大路家的云井尧觉所派出的刺客展开了激战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在激战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:00.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护打败了暗杀部队的首领贯井
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但石田和茶渡却受了重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.29,0:02:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着受了重伤的两人而动摇了的琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.26,0:02:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了中止这场纷争而一个人回到了尸魂界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来琉璃千代早就知道云井要暗杀自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护等人为了继承权问题
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闯入了琉璃千代的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.72,0:02:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.80,0:02:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺客...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:49.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.48,0:02:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一护
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止吧 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂队长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:05.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.28,0:03:19.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌乱 镇定点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.44,0:03:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为这里是哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢擅自闯入贵族的地盘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.44,0:03:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可轻饶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂队长 请您听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场婚礼和新首领就任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些本身就是无效的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能给我点时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们让你感到孤独无助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想保护你却反而将你逼入了绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明明知道你一直忍耐着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你也不需要全部一人承担下来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你已经下定决心的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也会陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不需要听云井的话的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.28,0:04:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是霞大路家真正的首领啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你一人无法完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.86,0:04:44.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也好 犬龙也好 猿龙也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露琪亚 井上 石田 茶渡也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是只身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你只要做你认为对的事情就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:17.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然敢对奴家如此无礼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.81,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊 琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还愣着干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快抓住这些乱党贼子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再扩大骚动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 快把他们逮住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 猿龙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要解放吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我说你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿龙 好强大的破坏力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:35.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他至今都未曾解放过斩魄刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:38.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露琪亚 琉璃千代人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:44.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你逃掉的 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我让开 朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我不让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:03.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开奴家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴家不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃千代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你振作点啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:10.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.19,0:07:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是琉璃千代的未婚夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙现在有些异常
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会察觉不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云井那家伙一定对琉璃千代做了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:26.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...我什么也...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神代行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...是假的吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃她...难道说...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底知不知道自己在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,箇中缘由容我日后相告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您让我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了 黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 这里太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为你是个值得敬重的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.19,0:09:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我是看走眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别狡辩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.03,0:09:30.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大前田副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们竟敢把我...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事情我才不想知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:48.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.10,0:09:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木大人 快趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:51.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 我绝不饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.96,0:09:58.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这样 可千万别放手啊 猿龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:09:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快放开 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绽放烂漫吧 红枝垂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:23.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个琉璃千代是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么证据
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...你一定要相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.37,0:10:29.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种谎话你到底要说到何时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.62,0:10:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用空手搏击的战斗你还不太习惯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:58.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你还想再吃点苦头嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽敌螯杀 雀蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:13.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本想尽可能不解放斩魄刀解决事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.41,0:11:17.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凌舞吧 袖白雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.48,0:11:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次之舞 白涟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.12,0:11:59.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.14,0:12:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边比较安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.61,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些死神要追过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.31,0:12:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及朽木露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:27.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有出去的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是逃进宅邸里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.07,0:12:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将还能行动的人集中起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.87,0:12:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重编队伍去追他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.18,0:12:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个家伙要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.13,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们俩等下再办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在优先抓捕黑崎和朽木
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.48,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂队长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要派人进入府邸内啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云井尧觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:13:01.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那些贼子会由我府上的人赶出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他们跑出来就请您抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂队长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.69,0:13:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是对上等贵族最基本的尊重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:30.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这里来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时就没有问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们来了 大家都很慌张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菅之木愁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是琉璃千代的未婚夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想帮琉璃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的琉璃到底在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:58.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃她发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你镇定一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.78,0:14:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.76,0:14:05.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是琉璃的未婚夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想保护琉璃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听了你刚才的一番话 我有所感悟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:18.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:24.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和琉璃的婚事是家里擅自决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.50,0:14:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从第一次见到她的时候开始就喜欢上她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.97,0:14:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必多礼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:38.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是菅之木愁大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琉璃的立场艰难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这连我也看得出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.53,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:52.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是让琉璃她那么孤独无助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.57,0:14:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在帮她也为时不晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起保护琉璃千代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但首先得从这里逃出去才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是府邸周围应该有碎蜂他们包围着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:27.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云井还没有来联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道他们家族是多大的贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,府邸实在是太大了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞这么大到底要干嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大前田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这些不知轻重的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说刚才抓住的人怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:58.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好绑着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好盯着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护他们可能会来救他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.00,0:16:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会自己闯入我们的包围圈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报告
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后门发现黑崎一护和朽木露琪亚的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.14,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.69,0:16:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们抓了菅之木愁大人做人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.04,0:16:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不但破坏婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.77,0:16:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还敢挟持人质
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎蜂队长 这是...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露琪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 碎蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你让开道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:16:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.01,0:17:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别追过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.82,0:17:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.73,0:17:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朽木和一护竟然会...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.45,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个... 黑崎一护是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 天贝队长并不认识他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做死神代行的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们来说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也算是恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神代行？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这样的人存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护和朽木露琪亚两人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挟持了菅之木家之子 菅之木愁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.26,0:17:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在瀞灵廷内逃窜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在二番队正在进行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但考虑黑崎一护的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.45,0:17:56.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为有必要增派人手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:17:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是这样 那就由我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他和各位有很深的交情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.67,0:18:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以一定很难下手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:08.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准天贝队长的提案
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.72,0:18:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瀞灵廷内紧急戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以二番 三番队为中心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.43,0:18:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对死神代行黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及十三番队朽木露琪亚进行追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 总队长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.97,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霞大路家的重臣云井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然请求我们出动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又不让我们进入府邸内
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他异样的警戒心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和多处可疑点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他与黑崎一护之间似乎有些过节
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.74,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉良 已有联络了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:19:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都已经做好准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:02.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神代行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.03,0:19:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对你们来说 可能有点难下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这是为了守护尸魂界秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 准备出动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.56,0:19:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.64,0:19:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑崎一护出现的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是霞大路家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有报告过来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有话的话你就直说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个... 我一直在想该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.63,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想还是告诉队长比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上这之前我看到贵船三席
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.27,0:19:54.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进出霞大路家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.15,0:19:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.16,0:19:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我问他本人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他却否定自己进出那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想队长可能还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.62,0:20:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前贵船三席也曾有过可疑的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无犹豫地对同伴刀剑相向
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战斗结束时不知在记录什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:29.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他平和的表面完全相反的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.06,0:20:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个贵船怎么可能会...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:34.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事情我以前都没有听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.55,0:20:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而现在贵船进出的霞大路家又发生事件
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本人在隐藏着自己和霞大路家的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.98,0:20:45.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一定有某些...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要下定论还为时过早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他和霞大路家有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的状态下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也还不能说他有什么问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:03.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这种状态下有这种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也难怪你会觉得有问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:08.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉良
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事你和别人说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 和谁都没说过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的直觉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.69,0:21:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次事件可能还有很多内幕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要暗中注意贵船的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一有问题就马上来告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.87,0:21:37.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在先去抓住黑崎一护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的以后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有能简单地抓住死神代行他们的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.79,0:23:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打出悬赏金 征集情报怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.50,0:23:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还真是个好办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶快准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那悬赏金哪里出
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.65,0:23:44.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来出钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神图鉴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 射场会长
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.05,0:24:10.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在考虑为了不让女性死神协会瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是否能请一位大牌的死神来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要我去问问看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.93,0:24:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我们希望你也能来做理事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.12,0:24:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
